quran[8]{c,v,t,f}:
  43,88,"Ọ̀rọ̀ (tí Ànábì - kí ìkẹ́ àti ọlà Allāhu máa bá a - ń sọ fún Allāhu ni pé): “Olúwa Mi, dájúdájú àwọn wọ̀nyí ni ìjọ tí kò gbàgbọ́.”"
  43,89,"Nítorí náà, ṣàmójú kúrò fún wọn, kí ó sì sọ pé: “Àlàáfíà!” Láìpẹ́ wọ́n máa mọ̀."
  50,13,"Àti àwọn ‘Ād, Fir‘aon àti àwọn ọmọ ìyá (Ànábì) Lūt,"
  50,14,"àti àwọn ará ’Aekah àti àwọn ìjọ Tubba‘u; gbogbo wọn pe àwọn Òjíṣẹ́ ní òpùrọ́. Nítorí náà, ìlérí Mi sì kò (lórí wọn)."
  50,15,"Ǹjẹ́ ìṣẹ̀dá àkọ́kọ́ kó agara bá Wa bí? Rárá, wọ́n wà nínú iyèméjì (àti ìrújú) nípa ìṣẹ̀dá (wọn) ní ọ̀tun ni."
  51,7,"Allāhu tún fi sánmọ̀ ọlọ́ṣọ̀ọ́ tó gún régé búra."
  51,8,"Dájúdájú ẹ̀yin wà lórí ọ̀rọ̀ tó ń takora wọn (nípa al-Ƙur’ān)."
  51,9,"Ẹni tí wọ́n ń ṣẹ́ lórí kúrò níbi al-Ƙur’ān ni ẹni tí Wọ́n ti ṣẹ́ lórí kúrò níbẹ̀ (láti inú Laohul-Mahfūṭḥ)."